The '''Ghi trade language''' was an artificial [[Language/Legends|language]] developed by [[Merchant/Legends|traders]] and [[Smuggler/Legends|smugglers]]. It was used to communicate with each other, and at the same time not being understood by anyone that could be spying. Its usefulness is unknown.

